Maxam Fund May Appeal Ruling Barring Suit Against Madoff Trustee

-- B y   L i n d a   S a n d l e r
-- 
2011-10-14T16:08:55Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-14/maxam-fund-may-appeal-ruling-barring-suit-against-madoff-trustee.html
Maxam Absolute Return Fund Ltd.,
ordered to stop its lawsuit against the liquidator of Bernard L.
Madoff’s firm, told a judge it is “likely” to appeal the
ruling, according to a court filing today.  Maxam sued trustee  Irving Picard  in the Cayman Islands
after he demanded return of $100 million taken out of the Ponzi
scheme.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Linda Sandler in New York at 
 lsandler@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
